{"about_the_game":"A citybuilder inspired by classics such as Ceasar III, Anno, Pharaoh and others which takes place the bottom of the ocean. The surface has become uninhabitable and raybomb radiation has turned many into mutants. It is your job to set up your underwater empire and guide new humanity to greatness!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/extras/600w-colony.png?t=1718289085\" /><br><br><strong>Goal of the game</strong><br><br>Your job is to keep everyone in your colony healthy and alive. Tend to all your people's needs; food, power, shelter, survival, safety, culture and entertainment.<br><br>If your people are happy your city grows and they have babies. If your people are deprived of food they die. Houses evolve if needs are met, increasing your population capacity. <br><br>The threat of raybomb mutants lurks around every corner and add another layer to the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/extras/600w-economy.png?t=1718289085\" /><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br>Find resource nodes, plan the layout of your colony, raise prosperity and culture ratings and keep your people safe!<br><br>Once your city is thriving and objectives are met, your success means your superiors will entrust you with repeating the process in a more challenging area. Along the way you unlock new buildings, resources and technologies to help with this.<br><br>At the end players will get to relive those epic childhood games while newer generation players get eased into this type of game so that they too can build fond memories.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/extras/600w-utility.png?t=1718289085\" /><br><br><strong>Campaign</strong><br><br>During the campaign you will be trading with other settlements and expanding your empire. <br><br>There are rival factions that will attempt the same and might reclaim your other cities if you don\u2019t watch out.<br><br>The goal is to move through various campaign scenarios that have various objectives.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718289085","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/page.bg.jpg?t=1718289085","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1718289085","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1718289085","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"A citybuilder inspired by classics such as Ceasar III, Anno, Pharaoh and others which takes place the bottom of the ocean. The surface has become uninhabitable and raybomb radiation has turned many into mutants. It is your job to set up your underwater empire and guide new humanity to greatness!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/extras/600w-colony.png?t=1718289085\" /><br><br><strong>Goal of the game</strong><br><br>Your job is to keep everyone in your colony healthy and alive. Tend to all your people's needs; food, power, shelter, survival, safety, culture and entertainment.<br><br>If your people are happy your city grows and they have babies. If your people are deprived of food they die. Houses evolve if needs are met, increasing your population capacity. <br><br>The threat of raybomb mutants lurks around every corner and add another layer to the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984470/extras/600w-economy.png?t=1718289085\" /><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br>Find resource nodes, plan the layout of yo